* Schema Management\nBest Practices
** Documentation
***_ Store schemas in version control
***_ Track alongside pipeline code
***_ Clear reference for change impact
** Alerting
***_ Notify on schema drift detection
***_ Even when handled automatically
***_ Understand evolving data patterns
** Naming Conventions
***_ Standardize column names
***_ Reduce case-sensitivity issues
***_ Predictable schema validation
** Testing
***_ Test schema handling in dev
***_ Edge cases with test data
***_ Verify before production deploy
** Tradeoffs
*** Strict enforcement
****_ Catches problems early
****_ Higher maintenance
*** Flexible evolution
****_ Less operational overhead
****_ Risk of unexpected changes
@endmindmap
